Name: Dawson
Description:
The Division of Dawson consists of:

  • part of the Burdekin Shire Council,
  • part of the Mackay Regional Council,
  • part of the Townsville City Council, and
  • part of the Whitsunday Regional Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Various small crops, prawn and fish farms, sugar growing and refining, beef cattle, coal mining related industries, abattoirs and tourism.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of Andrew Dawson, 1863-1910, Premier of Queensland (1899-1903).
